trans-unit.source: Represents a collection of <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.PolylineAnnotation" /> or <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.PolygonAnnotation" /> path points, which can be accessed using the <c>GraphicPathPoints</c> property.
trans-unit.target: 代表可以使用 <c>GraphicPathPoints</c> 屬性存取的 <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.PolylineAnnotation" /> 或 <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.PolygonAnnotation" /> 路徑端點集合。

trans-unit.source: This collection is used at design time only, and employs serialization to expose the shape of a polyline or polygon annotation, using their respective `GraphicPathPoints` collection properties.
trans-unit.target: 這個集合僅使用於設計階段，並採用公開聚合線條或多邊形註解中，使用其各自的形狀序列化`GraphicPathPoints`集合屬性。

trans-unit.source: At run time, use the `GraphicsPath` property to set the path of a <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.PolylineAnnotation> or <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.PolygonAnnotation>.
trans-unit.target: 在執行階段，使用`GraphicsPath`屬性來設定的路徑<xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.PolylineAnnotation>或<xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.PolygonAnnotation>。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.AnnotationPathPointCollection" /> class with the specified polyline annotation.
trans-unit.target: 使用指定的聚合線條註解，初始化 <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.AnnotationPathPointCollection" /> 類別的新執行個體。

trans-unit.source: <see langword="True" /> to release both unmanaged and managed resources; <see langword="false" /> to release only unmanaged resources.
trans-unit.target: <see langword="True" /> 表示釋放 Unmanaged 和 Managed 資源，<see langword="false" /> 表示只釋放 Unmanaged 資源。

trans-unit.source: Releases unmanaged and, optionally, managed resources.
trans-unit.target: 釋放 Unmanaged 和 Managed 資源 (後者為選擇性釋放)。

trans-unit.source: Forces the invalidation of the chart element.
